Problem Statement
  Appointment scheduling without a online aspect is difficult and leads to scheduling conflicts. 
  Customers need an easy way to view what times are available without having to call the shop.
  With an online appointment system, the barbers could focus more on cutting hair and less on scheduling appointments by phone, thereby increasing productivity.
  This online system would allow customers to view available times and be able to book appointments by barber.
  
Assumptions
  Scheduling appointments by phone during the work day reduces productivity.
  There sometimes exists conflicts that result from the current scheduling method.
  The clients of the business will understand the system and convert smoothly
  The manager will keep the system updated with accurate times that each barber is working
  
